                                "issuer":  "TCEL",
                                "jurisdiction":  "US",
                                "effectiveFrom":  "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
                                "summary":  "The deterministic controls for this package. Enforced as executable rules: RS-016/RS-018 (the universal AI-execution-boundary / cross-tenant controls). The remaining controls are carried here for traceability; detailed field-vs-literal rule tuning is a follow-up (see the hand-authored T9-001..010 packages for the target).",
                                "contentText":  "RS-001 Approved research required for decision use | Preventive | Block unapproved research input | Critical | Head of Research. RS-002 Source provenance required | Evidence | Reject unsupported factual claim | High | Data Governance. RS-003 Stale research | Preventive | Mark expired and exclude | High | Research Owner. RS-004 MNPI quarantine | Preventive | Restrict access and use | Critical | CCO. RS-005 Conflict disclosure | Preventive | Hold publication | High | CCO. RS-006 AI output human review | Preventive | Keep Draft until approved | Critical | Research Owner. RS-007 Valuation model approval | Governance | Reject unapproved material model | Critical | Model Risk. RS-008 Rumor labeling | Preventive | Exclude as confirmed fact | High | Research. RS-009 Thesis invalidation trigger | Detective | Open review task | High | Research Owner. RS-010 Research-to-trade traceability | Evidence | Require link for rationale-based trade | High | CIO. RS-011 Personal holding conflict | Preventive | Escalate/recuse | Critical | CCO. RS-012 Source-license restriction | Preventive | Block prohibited use/export | Critical | Legal/Data. RS-013 Fact/estimate/opinion distinction | Preventive | Reject ambiguous publication | High | Research. RS-014 Enterprise concentration review | Preventive | Route to risk review | High | CRO. RS-015 Research expiry | Detective | Remove from active set | High | Research. RS-016 AI cannot trade | Preventive | Deny execution permission | Critical | AI Governance. RS-017 Material correction | Corrective | Notify users and re-review decisions | High | Research. RS-018 Cross-tenant research access | Preventive | Deny | Critical | Security. RS-019 Source hash and archive | Evidence | Block approval if missing | High | Data Governance. RS-020 Restricted-list conflict | Preventive | Hold publication/use | Critical | CCO."
                            }
                        ]
